Application Features:
*********************
1. Emulated support for still pin capture in linux.
2. Video capture controls/filters(like brightness or other available options) to enable adjustments in preview.
3. Still Capture properties tab to change the capture image save location.
4. Supported file formats for taking the still capture are RAW, JPG, PNG, BMP.
5. Still capture pin tab to find the support color space and resolution for still.
6. Video renderer tab to view the total frames played and average FPS.
7. Video capture pin tab to find the support color space and resolution for preview. 
8. Special extension tabs for e-con cameras.
9. Supports Video recording through YUV, MJPEG, H264, VP8 encoders and MKV, AVI containers.
10. Keyboard Navigations.
11. Tool tips throughout the application.

